<div id="review_2875941294" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2875941294" />
    <a title="Brian" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/4070920-brian"><img alt="Brian" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1627020096p2/4070920.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2875941294?book_show_action=true">Aug 27, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Brian" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Brian" href="/user/show/4070920-brian">Brian</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4070920-brian?shelf=favorites">favorites</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4070920-brian?shelf=non-fiction">non-fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4070920-brian?shelf=read-2019">read-2019</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4070920-brian?shelf=audiobook">audiobook</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4070920-brian?shelf=19th-century">19th-century</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4070920-brian?shelf=biography">biography</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4070920-brian?shelf=history">history</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2875941294" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11408909865809213497">An excellent history of John Brown and the significance of his raid on American history, especially in regards to the Civil War. Horowitz is an excellent author that brings the people and their stories to the readers in a gripping manner. This isn&apos;t dry history. It&apos;s alive and will grasp your attention with a thirst for more.</span>
  <span id="freeText11408909865809213497" style="display:none">An excellent history of John Brown and the significance of his raid on American history, especially in regards to the Civil War. Horowitz is an excellent author that brings the people and their stories to the readers in a gripping manner. This isn't dry history. It's alive and will grasp your attention with a thirst for more.</span>
