<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/35224674-the-field-of-blood"><img alt="The Field of Blood: Violence in Congress and the Road to Civil War" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1503128798l/35224674._SX98_.jpg" />
