<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/53487129-the-york-patrol"><img alt="The York Patrol: The Real Story of Alvin York and the Unsung Heroes Who Made Him World War I&#39;s Most Famous Soldier" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1597694128l/53487129._SX98_.jpg" />
